{
  "category": "子法",
  "title": "勞動部積欠工資墊償基金管理委員會組織規程",
  "last_modified_date": "2023-02-15",
  "articles": [
    {
      "id": "WAGE_ARREARS_FUND_COMM_ORG-1",
      "chapter_no": null,
      "chapter_name": null,
      "article_no": "1",
      "summary": null,
      "content": "本規程依勞動基準法第二十八條第六項規定訂定之。",
      "url": "https://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawSingle.aspx?pcode=N0000010&flno=1",
      "related_concepts": []
    },
    {
      "id": "WAGE_ARREARS_FUND_COMM_ORG-2",
      "chapter_no": null,
      "chapter_name": null,
      "article_no": "2",
      "summary": null,
      "content": "(1)勞動部積欠工資墊償基金（以下簡稱本基金）管理委員會（以下簡稱本會），置委員十三人至十五人，其中一人為主任委員，由勞動部次長一人兼任之；其餘委員，由勞動部就下列人員派（聘）兼之：\n一、勞動部代表一人。\n二、經濟部代表一人。\n三、財政部代表一人。\n四、直轄市或縣（市）政府代表二人。\n五、勞方代表二人。\n六、資方代表二人。\n七、專家學者三人至五人。\n(2)本會之委員，任一性別比例不得少於三分之一。",
      "url": "https://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawSingle.aspx?pcode=N0000010&flno=2",
      "related_concepts": []
    },
    {
      "id": "WAGE_ARREARS_FUND_COMM_ORG-3",
      "chapter_no": null,
      "chapter_name": null,
      "article_no": "3",
      "summary": null,
      "content": "本會委員任期二年，期滿得續聘之。但代表機關或團體出任者，應隨其本職進退。",
      "url": "https://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawSingle.aspx?pcode=N0000010&flno=3",
      "related_concepts": []
    },
    {
      "id": "WAGE_ARREARS_FUND_COMM_ORG-4",
      "chapter_no": null,
      "chapter_name": null,
      "article_no": "4",
      "summary": null,
      "content": "(1)本會之任務如下：\n一、本基金年度計畫及業務報告之審議事項。\n二、本基金業務之檢討改進事項。\n三、本基金年度預算、決算之審議事項。\n四、本基金收支之審核事項。\n五、其他事項。\n(2)本會不對外行文，其決議事項應報請勞動部核定後分別辦理。",
      "url": "https://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawSingle.aspx?pcode=N0000010&flno=4",
      "related_concepts": []
    },
    {
      "id": "WAGE_ARREARS_FUND_COMM_ORG-5",
      "chapter_no": null,
      "chapter_name": null,
      "article_no": "5",
      "summary": null,
      "content": "本會置執行秘書一人，由勞動部勞動條件及就業平等司司長兼任；置辦事人員若干人，由勞動部派兼之。本會行政管理事項，由勞動部統籌，涉及人事、預決算、財產管理之監督等業務，由各權責單位辦理。",
      "url": "https://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawSingle.aspx?pcode=N0000010&flno=5",
      "related_concepts": []
    },
    {
      "id": "WAGE_ARREARS_FUND_COMM_ORG-6",
      "chapter_no": null,
      "chapter_name": null,
      "article_no": "6",
      "summary": null,
      "content": "(1)本會以每六個月開會一次為原則，必要時得舉行臨時會議，均由主任委員召集之。\n(2)委員應親自出席會議，不得委託他人代理出席。",
      "url": "https://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawSingle.aspx?pcode=N0000010&flno=6",
      "related_concepts": []
    },
    {
      "id": "WAGE_ARREARS_FUND_COMM_ORG-7",
      "chapter_no": null,
      "chapter_name": null,
      "article_no": "7",
      "summary": null,
      "content": "本會開會應有二分之一以上委員出席，其決議事項應經出席委員三分之二以上同意行之。",
      "url": "https://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawSingle.aspx?pcode=N0000010&flno=7",
      "related_concepts": []
    },
    {
      "id": "WAGE_ARREARS_FUND_COMM_ORG-8",
      "chapter_no": null,
      "chapter_name": null,
      "article_no": "8",
      "summary": null,
      "content": "本會開會時，得邀請勞動部勞工保險局及有關單位人員列席。",
      "url": "https://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawSingle.aspx?pcode=N0000010&flno=8",
      "related_concepts": []
    },
    {
      "id": "WAGE_ARREARS_FUND_COMM_ORG-9",
      "chapter_no": null,
      "chapter_name": null,
      "article_no": "9",
      "summary": null,
      "content": "本會委員為無給職。但非屬勞動部人員之委員，得依規定支給兼職費及交通費。",
      "url": "https://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawSingle.aspx?pcode=N0000010&flno=9",
      "related_concepts": []
    },
    {
      "id": "WAGE_ARREARS_FUND_COMM_ORG-10",
      "chapter_no": null,
      "chapter_name": null,
      "article_no": "10",
      "summary": null,
      "content": "本規程自發布日施行。",
      "url": "https://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawSingle.aspx?pcode=N0000010&flno=10",
      "related_concepts": []
    }
  ]
}